data.description: Welcome Home in Spring Meadows! This spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence boasts a terrific blend of comfort and style, offering a lifestyle of convenience and relaxation.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the inviting laminate and engineered hardwood flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the home, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The abundance of natural light floods the interior, enhancing the sense of space and tranquility.  The home features numerous updates, including new windows installed in 2021, ensuring energy efficiency and modern aesthetics. The roof was replaced in 2018, providing peace of mind and protection for years to come. In 2019, both the kitchen and bathrooms were tastefully updated, showcasing contemporary finishes and thoughtful design.  The kitchen serves as the heart of the home, boasting granite countertops and ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a joyous experience. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet meal with family, this kitchen is sure to impress.  With leased to own solar panels, you'll enjoy the benefits of sustainable living while reducing your carbon footprint and utility bills. The practicality of a 1 car garage adds convenience to your daily routine, providing secure parking and storage space.  Escape to the expansive backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding. Additionally, the main floor laundry room adds functionality and ease to your lifestyle.  Located in the desirable community of Spring Meadows and with no monthly HOA fees, this townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and affordability. Don't miss your opportunity to make this your new home sweet home! Schedule your showing today.  **This home does come with a transferrable Choice Home Warranty valid until 8-8-2029!**
